Title: Our 'Cops' is On
Plot: It's a trip down memory lane for Earl, Randy, Joy, Darnell and the Crab Shack regulars when they remember their fifteen minutes of fame watching a 2003 repeat of the TV show "Cops," which was filmed in Camden County.
GuestStars: Pramod Kumar,  Silas Weir Mitchell,  Bill Suplee,  Timothy Stack,  Maxie J. Santillan Junior,  George Frangides,  Mike O'Malley,  Kathy Kinney
